### Neue Bestellung anlegen
POST http://localhost:8080/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerName": "Chris Muster",
  "customerEmail": "chris@example.com",
  "shippingAddress": "Musterstraße 12, 8020 Graz",
  "kitName": "AC Milan 2007 Home",
  "quantity": 2,
  "unitPrice": 89.99
}

### Alle Bestellungen abrufen
GET http://localhost:8080/api/orders

### Einzelne Bestellung abrufen
GET http://localhost:8080/api/orders/1

### Bestellung bezahlen
POST http://localhost:8080/api/orders/1/pay

### Bestellung verpacken
POST http://localhost:8080/api/orders/1/pack

### Bestellung versenden
POST http://localhost:8080/api/orders/1/ship
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "trackingNumber": "TRACK-2026-001"
}

### Bestellung stornieren
POST http://localhost:8080/api/orders/1/cancel
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reason": "Kunde hat sich umentschieden"
}

### Bestellung retournieren
POST http://localhost:8080/api/orders/1/return
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reason": "Größe passt nicht"
}

### Bestellungen nach Status abrufen
GET http://localhost:8080/api/orders/status/SHIPPED